* RCTVIEW is a native Component 

* A lot of nested components become a performance bottle neck

* Style simple object creates the style object every time. With Stylesheet it caches it

* FlexBox in React Native is column by default

* react-native-vector-icons cool collection of icons

* use the same animated value for more animations

* use reanimated for best performance

